body.name: Native Union Belt Cable USB-C to USB-A - 4ft Ultra-Strong Charging Cable with Leather Strap Compatible with iPhone 15, Samsung Galaxy Z Fold 5, Flip 5 / S23 Ultra, Pixel 7 Pro, iPad Pro (Cosmos)
deliveryMessages: FREE delivery Monday, February 19 on orders shipped by Amazon over $35
Or fastest delivery Thursday, February 15. Order within 8 hrs 35 mins
features: MADE FOR USB-C / TYPE-C DEVICES: Charge and sync your USB-C device from USB-A ports. Compatible with iPhone 15, 15 Plus, 15 Pro, 15 Pro Max, iPad Pro (2018 and later), iPad Air 4 (2020), iPad Air 5 (2022), iPad mini 6 (2021), Galaxy Z Flip 5, Z Fold 5, S23, S23+, S23 Ultra or before model; Google Pixel 8, 8 Pro, Motorola Moto G Power, Moto G Stylus, Moto Edge, Moto Plus, Moto Razr (2022) and all other USB-C Devices

ULTRA-STRONG: Durable nylon braided cable featuring a reinforced structure crafted with DuPont Kevlar fiber for unparalleled strength, compatible with all USB-C devices - safely experience high speed charging up to 2.4 Amps

EXTENDED LIFESPAN: O-Flex strain relief design at connector joint provides controlled flexibility to absorb 2 x more stress than regular strain relief. Its 10,000+ bend* lifespan makes it 6 x stronger than standard Lightning cables

TANGLE-FREE STYLE: Simply wrap up your cable with the integrated genuine leather strap to keep your 4-foot cable neat, tangle-free and in good condition. Slide the belt anywhere along the cable for easy carry

LIFETIME LIMITED WARRANTY: The Lifetime Limited Warranty will cover any defect in materials or workmanship under normal use conditions, for as long as the customer owns the cable - Please refer to the manufacturer’s website for full terms and conditions.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 23, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Sturdy and fast
reviews.reviewText: Great cord. Have purchased 3 because they last forever and are good quality.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 4, 2023
reviews.reviewText: Good cable for traveling. I usually keep it in a backpack pocket with my anker 20000mah battery. It works fine with my samsung speedcharger block for charging my phone. No complaints.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on July 22, 2019
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great quality and nice looks
reviews.reviewText: My wireless products require too many wires. I know right? But when they do, I prefer Native Union. Nice looking and durable. They have to be for me. I am as forgetful as anything and will pick up my phone still hooked to the cable and walk off. Or get out of my truck with the stupid thing still plugged in. Native Union works for me. The cable is tough, yet still pliable to be functional. I have bought a few in the past that were so thick they didn't bend as you use the product. I have the belted Lightnening Cable and have used it for over a year without an issue. I just bought the belted C and it's quality matches the Lightening cable. I also have their multi, function Ligntening, Micro USB, USB C and it's long, but the trade off is good having all three in one cable.

reviews.reviewText: It was cheaper than what Apple wants to charge you for a cord and I went for it...its working marvelously!!!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 11, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars The best charging cord I've ever used. It's worth the price
reviews.reviewText: Unlike other cords, this one is built to endure. I have an older phone that doesn't like to take a charge, but when I plugged in this cord not only did it take the charge, it did so in fast charging mode~ something it hasn't done in years. Credit where credit is due: very nice craftsmanship, and it looks pretty cool too. I recommend it.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 13, 2023
reviews.reviewText: My original one was great until I let the usb-c end soak in muddy/salty water in the floor matt of my vehicle for a week or so. I learned a lesson.

Having bought many different brands of charging cords for our iPhones, this company produces the best. The cord is durable and connection is sturdy. Although the price is more than what I have paid for previously, the quality will prevent multiple buys (and adding to the landfill).
Cable has a nice design and is robust. Can’t go wrong with the brand.

Voilà un long moment que je l'utilise.Il est toujours en très bon état, solide avec un beau design et est conforme à la photo.Aussi, rien de plus pratique qu'un système d'attache pour le ranger convenablement.Je le recommande à toutes celles et tous ceux qui recherchent un bon câble.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the Netherlands on April 18, 2023

reviews.reviewText: Lo utilizzo da tempo,è rivestito da un tessuto intrecciato, che lo rende resistente e al contempo molto flessibile. La cura per i particolari di Native Union è evidente anche nel silicone che protegge le estremità, molto durevole.il prezzo è abbastanza alto, ma la qualità si paga, non sono cavi per chi vuole l’economicità, piuttosto per chi ricerca design, accuratezza nei dettagli e funzionalità aggiunte.
